Dependencies:

To run this program from source or to build into a binary, the following libraries are needed.
- Python v. 2.4+
- reportlab (for PDF production)
- easygui

The basic second check function can be performed with just the built in Python libraries. and run as:

python hdrcheck.py x-coord y-coord z-coord target-dose input-report-file-name

where coordinates are in cm and target dose is in Gy.
